Quickstrike:





Quickstrike chuckled lowly at KitKat. "That's what ah was thinkin'." he 
whispered back. "If they do somethin' stupid, ah'm throwin' their kiesters 
out in th' Wild. That might straighten 'em out."

At the mouth of the cave, he saw Terrorsaur fly enter in his beast mode. The 
dactyl had been out and about lately.
